title: Twitter Says Parts of Its Source Code Were Leaked Online
description: The leak adds to the challenges facing the Elon Musk-owned company, which is trying to unmask the person responsible and any other people who downloaded the code.

title: Elon Musk Values Twitter at $20 Billion
description: The billionaire bought the social media company for $44 billion in October and took it private.

title: At Apple, Rare Dissent Over a New Product: Interactive Goggles
description: The company is expected to unveil an augmented reality headset in a few months. Some employees wonder if the device makes sense for Apple.
